WEBVTT

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:45.799
You don't know,

00:00:47.320 --> 00:00:48.399
for so many years at Kaye Mountain,

00:00:48.759 --> 00:00:50.320
there hasn't been a single mistake.

00:00:50.799 --> 00:00:51.960
How could it suddenly be investigated?

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:55.399
The Five Dragons Challenge is imminent.

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:57.920
Naturally, I have no time to worry about a useless thing.

00:01:00.520 --> 00:01:02.079
The challenge is just around the corner.

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:03.200
You...

00:01:04.079 --> 00:01:05.519
don't cause any more trouble for me.

00:01:12.159 --> 00:01:12.959
Ha ha ha.

00:01:16.040 --> 00:01:16.840
How did you get in?

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:19.359
Don't worry about it.

00:01:22.280 --> 00:01:22.840
Guess.

00:01:23.239 --> 00:01:24.280
Guess what I...

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:25.519
came to find you for today?

00:01:25.799 --> 00:01:27.040
About Lang Jiu being wanted...

00:01:31.799 --> 00:01:32.719
don't worry about it.

00:01:37.239 --> 00:01:37.920
What are you doing?

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:39.120
Get down.

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:40.959
Get down!

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:42.280
Have you lost your mind?

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:43.599
I won't come down.

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:44.480
If you don't come down right now,

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:45.799
don't come to my house ever again.

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:50.200
You're really not loyal, are you?

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:53.480
From the yacht to Kaye Mountain,

00:01:53.599 --> 00:01:54.719
I transformed into...

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:56.280
a Champion of Justice.

00:01:56.519 --> 00:01:57.200
Using...

00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:00.040
my beauty, bravery, and wisdom,

00:02:00.439 --> 00:02:02.480
I recorded key evidence of the transaction,

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:03.079
exposed Lang Jiu,

00:02:03.079 --> 00:02:04.159
and when I saved those girls,

00:02:04.159 --> 00:02:05.519
you didn't have this attitude!

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:06.359
Besides,

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.159
I'm looking for you today...

00:02:08.439 --> 00:02:09.400
for serious business.

00:02:13.199 --> 00:02:14.199
Look, what is this?

00:02:16.639 --> 00:02:18.520
An invitation to the Five Dragons Challenge.

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:20.319
Five million.

00:02:22.159 --> 00:02:22.840
Where did you get it?

00:02:23.199 --> 00:02:24.280
You're allowed...

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:25.840
to have a double identity,

00:02:26.199 --> 00:02:27.280
but I'm not allowed to have one?

00:02:28.039 --> 00:02:29.360
To tell you the truth,

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:31.199
I am...

00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:33.800
the sole successor of the Chaoli Group,

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:35.560
Li Yi.

00:02:37.039 --> 00:02:38.120
Getting an invitation...

00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:39.759
is a piece of cake.

00:02:40.199 --> 00:02:42.400
Then the Billiards Association Chairman Li Chaoli is your...

00:02:42.759 --> 00:02:43.639
That old antique...

00:02:43.919 --> 00:02:44.840
is my grandfather.

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:47.199
The new Chairman, Li Hongbin,

00:02:47.599 --> 00:02:48.400
is my dad.

00:02:48.599 --> 00:02:49.680
It's just because those two...

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.199
insisted on an arranged marriage for me,

00:02:51.520 --> 00:02:52.120
that I...

00:02:52.280 --> 00:02:54.080
changed my name and ran away from home.

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:56.800
You kept it well hidden.

00:02:59.319 --> 00:03:00.800
But you helped me a lot this time.

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:02.919
Thank you.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:04.759
It's nothing.

00:03:05.719 --> 00:03:06.680
Then I'm going to take a shower.

00:03:12.439 --> 00:03:13.360
You're taking a shower at my house?

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:14.800
Have you lost your mind again?

00:03:15.319 --> 00:03:16.719
Idol,

00:03:17.439 --> 00:03:20.240
this lady got you such a crucial thing.

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:22.719
According to etiquette,

00:03:24.599 --> 00:03:26.319
shouldn't you offer yourself in marriage?

00:03:27.360 --> 00:03:28.120
I'll take you back.

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:30.759
I'm not going back.

00:03:30.759 --> 00:03:32.199
Why does a girl always run to a man's house?

00:03:32.199 --> 00:03:33.039
I'm not going back.

00:03:33.039 --> 00:03:33.840
How improper!

00:03:49.800 --> 00:03:50.840
What's the situation?

00:03:50.960 --> 00:03:52.439
She got kidnapped right after being sent home?

00:03:58.280 --> 00:03:59.159
What have you done to her?

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:00.360
She...

00:04:00.520 --> 00:04:01.960
should still be safe, I guess.

00:04:02.599 --> 00:04:05.039
Didn't expect this little girl to be a money tree.

00:04:05.199 --> 00:04:06.879
I'm counting on her to help me run away.

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:07.560
Lang Jiu,

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:08.400
I'm telling you,

00:04:08.759 --> 00:04:09.919
you have nowhere left to go.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:10.879
You'd better let her go.

00:04:11.039 --> 00:04:12.280
It's not too late to turn yourself in now.

00:04:12.759 --> 00:04:13.520
Cut the crap.

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:16.160
Tell Chaoli Group to bring five million in cash.

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:18.240
Otherwise, don't blame me if I kill the hostage.

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:19.199
The money is not a problem.

00:04:19.399 --> 00:04:20.240
Don't you hurt her.

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:32.199
Ke'er

00:04:32.959 --> 00:04:33.920
You actually tricked me.

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:40.879
Blame yourself for being too naive.

00:04:41.439 --> 00:04:43.279
Blame that Hei Ba for not knowing his place.

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:46.920
Going against me won't end well for you.

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:49.040
Lang Jiu.

00:04:50.399 --> 00:04:52.519
Do you have any moves other than kidnapping?

00:04:53.560 --> 00:04:54.639
You have zero creativity.

00:04:55.199 --> 00:04:56.360
You're out of tricks, aren't you?

00:04:56.680 --> 00:04:57.759
None of your business what moves I use.

00:04:58.480 --> 00:04:59.319
As long as it works.

00:05:07.959 --> 00:05:09.120
I'll deal with you later.

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:11.279
Good job.

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.759
Here is your payment.

00:05:23.319 --> 00:05:24.160
Take the money.

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:25.759
Get far away from here.

00:05:26.879 --> 00:05:27.800
Don't blab.

00:05:28.879 --> 00:05:29.680
Or else...

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.040
You know the consequences.

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:40.160
Lin Lu.

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:41.279
I...

00:05:41.959 --> 00:05:43.439
I... I'm sorry.

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:46.439
Don't go.

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:49.240
Don't go.

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.399
Enough.

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:53.279
Once your family's money arrives,

00:05:53.920 --> 00:05:55.160
I'll let you go.

00:06:20.439 --> 00:06:20.959
Hey.

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:23.439
Ke'er.

00:06:40.519 --> 00:06:41.319
Shh.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:44.480
Yi Xin.

00:06:44.839 --> 00:06:46.360
Ke'er told me your location.

00:06:46.439 --> 00:06:47.399
I'm here to get you out.

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:50.240
Let's go.

00:06:50.800 --> 00:06:51.279
Hurry.

00:06:51.519 --> 00:06:52.279
Catch them!

00:06:58.720 --> 00:06:59.240
You go first.

00:06:59.439 --> 00:07:00.160
I'll go distract them.

00:07:00.439 --> 00:07:01.519
But what about you?

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:02.240
Don't worry.

00:07:02.439 --> 00:07:03.879
Lang Jiu doesn't have the guts to touch me.

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:05.120
Go, quickly!

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:17.079
Brother Jiu.

00:07:17.199 --> 00:07:18.000
Lin Lu ran away.

00:07:28.199 --> 00:07:30.319
It was you again, you witch.

00:07:30.519 --> 00:07:31.279
So what?

00:07:32.199 --> 00:07:33.120
Do you dare to touch me?

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:34.560
What?

00:07:35.279 --> 00:07:36.759
Want another broken leg?

00:07:38.279 --> 00:07:39.560
At a time like this,

00:07:39.560 --> 00:07:41.360
is there anything I wouldn't dare to do?

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:46.399
I think

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:49.680
it's better to just shut you up.

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:06.480
Go to hell!

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:51.840
Hei Ba!

00:08:53.759 --> 00:08:54.320
Hei Ba!

00:08:54.399 --> 00:08:55.000
Lin Lu.

00:08:55.279 --> 00:08:56.399
Go save Sister Yi Xin!

00:08:56.559 --> 00:08:57.240
What happened to her?

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:58.879
To save me,

00:08:59.039 --> 00:09:00.360
she lured Lang Jiu's men away.

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:01.879
She's still in the warehouse.

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:03.679
You go first.

00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:04.759
Leave it to me.

00:09:19.159 --> 00:09:20.240
Kill him for me!

00:09:31.399 --> 00:09:32.000
Brother, go!

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:32.799
Leave this to us.

00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:07.720
No!

00:10:16.919 --> 00:10:17.600
Don't!

00:10:28.279 --> 00:10:29.080
Don't!

00:10:59.360 --> 00:11:00.000
Hei Ba!